#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.normal:3
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.orthogonal:5
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.rotateBy:7
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.set:5
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.slerp:12
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.sub:5
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.transformAsNormal:5
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.xform4:7 of
msgid "`Vector`"
msgstr "`Vector`"

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:26
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.set:6 of
msgid "x, y, z, w"
msgstr "x, y, z, w"

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:27
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.set:7 of
msgid "x, y, z"
msgstr "x, y, z"

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:28
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.set:8 of
msgid "x, y"
msgstr "x, y"

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:29
#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector.set:9 of
msgid "4値までのシーケンス"
msgstr "Sequence up to 4 values"

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:32 of
msgid "w がこのような特殊な振る舞いをするのは、 API 等の他のオブジェクトとの可換性を確保するため。"
msgstr ""
"The reason why w behaves in this special way is to ensure interchangeability"
" with other objects such as APIs."

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:35 of
msgid ""
"w に 1 以外を明示しない限り、 :mayaapi2:`MVector` コンストラクタのように長さ 4 の "
"シーケンスを受け付けないものにも渡すことができる。"
msgstr ""
"Unless w is explicitly set to something other than 1, it can also be passed "
"to something that does not accept sequences of length 4, such as the "
":mayaapi2:`MVector` constructor."

#: cymel.core.datatypes.vector.Vector:39 of
msgid ""
"また、w に 1 以外を明示した場合は、:mayaapi2:`MPoint` や `list` などと交換した際にも、きちんとその情報が継承される。"
msgstr ""
"Also, if you specify a value other than 1 for w, that information will be "
"properly inherited even when exchanging with :mayaapi2:`MPoint` or `list`."

